HEADWORD: Testable
<hw>Test"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Testament</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Capable of being tested or
proved.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Capable of being devised, or given by
will.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

